Key to the Palaearctic species of 
<taxonomicName box="[559,647,511,537]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiliidae" genus="Ptiliola" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
